<F P=100> POLAND </F>
<H3> <TI>   Rightists Appeal for Ban </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2201202594 Warsaw TVP Television First Program Network in 
Polish 1830 GMT 22 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2201202594 </F>
<F P=104>  Warsaw TVP Television First Program Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Polish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Relayed by TV Polonia network] </F>
  [Text] The political council of the Movement for the 
Republic has decided to join the coalition, formed on 10 
November, of Center Accord, the Christian-National Union, and 
the Polish Peasant Party-Peasant Accord. The coalition of these 
four parties has approached the minister of foreign affairs 
demanding that Vladimir Zhirinovskiy, the leader of the Russian 
nationalists who is planning to visit us at the end of January, 
not be allowed into Poland. 

</TEXT>

