Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpts] Bosnian Army soldiers have achieved new 
successes on the Teocak front [eastern Bosnia]. Second Corps 
units have captured the Greben elevation. Many chetniks were 
killed in the operation and the bodies of eight of them were 
seized by our soldiers. A considerable amount of military 
equipment was also captured. 
  The chetniks have continued their offensive on the Maglaj 
front in the zone of responsibility of the Seven-South 
Operational Group [Bosnia-Herzegovina Army]. The size of the 
chetnik losses at this front is illustrated by the fact that 
yesterday our soldiers killed 70 and seriously or lightly 
wounded dozens of chetniks. [passage omitted] 
