<F P=100> BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Four Children Killed in Mostar Shelling </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2301172294 Mostar Croatian Radio Herceg-Bosna in 
Serbo-Croatian 1700 GMT 23 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2301172294 </F>
<F P=104>  Mostar Croatian Radio Herceg-Bosna </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Serbo-Croatian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] More than 100 120-mm mortar shells landed on the 
free [Croat-held] part of Mostar this afternoon. Four children 
were killed by the shells: Damir Rizvan, Armin Rizvan, Emanuela 
Meskic, and Emil Meskic. Four children and four adults were 
wounded, the command of the Mostar operational zone has reported. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

