<F P=100> POLAND </F>
<H3> <TI>   Russia's Zhirinovskiy To Visit 27 Jan </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2101214694 Warsaw TV Polonia Network in Polish 2000 GMT 21 
Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2101214694 </F>
<F P=104>  Warsaw TV Polonia Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Polish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Vladimir Zhirinovskiy, accompanied by a seven-member 
delegation, will arrive in Warsaw on Thursday, 27 January, at 
1000. Apart from Zhirinovskiy, the star of the delegation will 
no doubt be Aleksandr Vengerovskiy, who is of Polish descent and 
was recently elected as deputy chairman of the Duma. 

