<H3> <TI>   Environment Protection Accord Signed With Ukraine </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2401160194 Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network in Polish 1500 
GMT 24 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2401160194 </F>
<F P=104>  Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Polish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] Polish and Ukrainian Government representatives 
have signed in Warsaw an agreement on environmental protection 
and also an agreement on handling dangerous waste. Both states 
decided to eliminate mutual ecological dangers as soon as 
possible, Stanislaw Zelichowski, Minister for Environment 
Protection, Natural Resources and Forestry said. [passage 
omitted] 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

<DOC>
<DOCNO> FBIS3-50179 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "dreeu016_p_94010" </HT>


<HEADER>
