<F P=100> POLAND </F>
<H3> <TI>   Three More Provincial Governors Dismissed </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2601192494 Warsaw PAP in Polish 1603 GMT 26 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2601192494 </F>
<F P=104>  Warsaw PAP </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Polish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Warsaw, 26 Jan (PAP) -- The chairman of the Council 
of Ministers has dismissed the following voivodas: Stanislaw 
Czuba in Skierniewice with effect from 26 January, Eugeniusz 
Matyjas in Leszno with effect from 31 January, and Jerzy Orzel 
in Tarnow with effect from 31 January. This was reported by the 
government press office today. 
  The prime minister thanked the dismissed voivodas for their 
work in state administration. 

</TEXT>

