<H3> <TI>   Ukrainian Foreign Minister Visits </TI></H3>
<H4>   Meets With Valentic </H4>
<F P=102> LD2601222694 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in Serbo-Croatian 
2100 GMT 26 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2601222694 </F>
<F P=104>  Zagreb Radio Croatia Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Serbo-Croatian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Croatian Prime Minister Nikica Valentic also 
received Ukrainian Foreign Minister Anatoliy Zlenko. The 
Croatian prime minister briefed the Ukrainian foreign minister 
on the situation in the country, stressing that it was dependent 
on the war in Bosnia- Herzegovina and the general crisis in this 
region. Laying emphasis on Croatia's desire for peace, Valentic 
called on Ukraine -- as a respectable European country -- to 
help [Croatia] in its search for a way out of the crisis. 

</TEXT>

