GMT 27 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2701164894 </F>
<F P=104>  Prague Radiozurnal Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Czech </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Head of the Czech broadcasts of Radio Free Europe 
[RFE] Pavel Pechacek has praised the positive attitude of our 
government in the talks about the possible transfer of the 
station from Munich to Prague. The decision has not been made 
yet, Pavel Pechacek said, and added that further talks on the 
