have talks in Bratislava with the Slovak Government on Friday. 
According to Pechacek, the Slovak Government, in connection with 
its proposal to end the possibility of RFE broadcasts on Velke 
Kostolany, Poprad, and Presov transmitters, probably wants to 
offer an alternative solution. 

